TEMPLATE FOR CREATING A NEW POST

REQUEST TYPE: POST REQUEST

WHAT I USE TO TEST IN POSTMAN:

localhost:5050/api/journal/

CREATING A NEW JOURNAL POST (POST REQUEST)

endpoint: 
/newpost

{
    "id": "",
    "post": "",
    "family_code": "",
    "url": ""
}

UPDATING AN EXISTING JOURNAL POST (PUT REQUEST)

endpoint: 
/updatepost

{
    "post": "",
    "post_id": ""
}

// CREATE A COMMENT ON A JOURNAL POST (POST REQUEST)
endpoint: 

/newcomment
{
    "id": "",
    "post_id": "",
    "comment": "",
    "comment_id": "",
    "family_code": "",
    "url": ""
}

// UPDATING A COMMENT ON A JOUNRAL POST (PUT REQUEST)

endpoint: 
/updatecomment

{
    "comment": "",
    "comment_id": ""
}